Class CtsPersistenceOperationsMonitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.cts.monitoring.impl.persistence.CtsPersistenceOperationsMonitor

  • public class CtsPersistenceOperationsMonitor
extends Object
    This acts to control the interaction between the exposed monitoring endpoints and the CTS persistence store for queries based on a TokenType
